text: daembi a l laoh nung tabasnang phalbony da brasaer bamphot dl puokke nouv avei del puokke ban sang kanlongomk haey trong nung banthem aoy puokke leusa pi nih tiet daoy kar braosa bratan robsa trong . haey a l laoh nung phdal leaphosakkar champoh anaknea del trong mean chetnea daoy kmean karkamnt laey
